[Values for -webkit-user-drag attribute]
none: Do not allow this element to be dragged.
element: Allow this element to be dragged.
auto: Use the default logic for determining
whether the element should be dragged.
(Images, links, and text selections are the only elements that can be dragged.)
This is the default value.


